    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project lovers! This vehicle is the perfect project car for someone looking to roll up their sleeves and bring a classic back to life. While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic foundation for a full restoration or a valuable source of parts at a budget-friendly price. Grab this opportunity to build your dream ride from the ground up!",
