    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts as it should, making it a dependable choice for any driver. While the exterior is generally clean, you may find a few minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with regular use. The interior is tidy and comfortable, with only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Overall, this is a solid, honest car that offers a great balance of reliability and value.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical attention and cosmetic restoration. The engine currently runs roughly and may have underlying issues, while the transmission shifts are inconsistent. Externally, the body shows noticeable rust, several dents, and fading paint; the interior is heavily worn with tears in the upholstery and non-functioning electronics. It is best suited as a project car or for parts, and we recommend a professional inspection before purchase.",
      "price": 4500.0,
